Gentoo overlay for an experemental Apple cross-compiler based on LLVM clang.

To install: sudo curl https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kwhat/crossdev-apple-overlay/master/metadata/crossdev-apple-overlay.conf -O /etc/portage/repos.conf/crossdev-apple-overlay.conf

To add a toolchain: sudo crossdev --stage0 --binutils 4.6 --target i686-apple-darwin -P -v
